The Combine.name: The Combine
The Combine.description:
The Combine, often referred to as The Union, Our Benefactors, or simply by the abbreviation CMB, is a universal empire formed by numerous worlds and universes, that aims on unifying all Robloxians under one flag. They often do not show any mercy or emotions during their deployments, only caring about The Union and The Union only, while obviously caring about their fellow soldiers too.
Join us to help restore order in this "lovely" desert that we all know about.

--[What We Offer]--

- 3 main branches.
- 3 divisions with more possible divisions in the future.
- Cheap, optional uniforms (as cheap as possible).
- Fun events.
